<i>noun</i>: 반정 [반ː정] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>반정 [반ː정]</dt><br>
<dd>rectifying; restoring things to a proper state</dd><br>
<dd>(옛날에) 옳지 못한 임금을 밀어내고 새 임금을 세워 나라를 바로잡음.</dd><br>
<dd>(archaic) The act of forcing out an unjust king and putting a new king on the throne to restore proper order in a state.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>